    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Derailed</strong> - 第一人称心理恐怖游戏，属于“步行模拟”类别。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏平均时长：80分钟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/extras/7268b9497ef084a7d2eb56df4b9552dc.poster.avif?t=1759491646\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/extras/7268b9497ef084a7d2eb56df4b9552dc.webm?t=1759491646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/extras/7268b9497ef084a7d2eb56df4b9552dc.mp4?t=1759491646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雨滴敲打着漏水的屋顶，空气中弥漫着潮湿的气味。历经数十年风雨的墙壁、随风晃动的玻璃、空旷的脚步声——周围的一切似乎一遍又一遍地提醒你，这里不属于你。但你别无选择，唯一的道路就是向前。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/extras/98986c03448ee372378bf8a59da62763.poster.avif?t=1759491646\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/extras/98986c03448ee372378bf8a59da62763.webm?t=1759491646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/extras/98986c03448ee372378bf8a59da62763.mp4?t=1759491646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>游戏特色：</strong></i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >类型：“步行模拟”；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与物品互动，解开谜题以推动剧情发展；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开这个几乎被遗忘的车站中隐藏的秘密；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在细致入微的场景中，体验令人不安的氛围；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环绕3D音效，全面增强沉浸式体验；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏时长较短，适合一晚通关，保持紧张感直至结尾。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/extras/d798d57ac9e6b01a127f4ff2cead5f69.poster.avif?t=1759491646\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/extras/d798d57ac9e6b01a127f4ff2cead5f69.webm?t=1759491646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/extras/d798d57ac9e6b01a127f4ff2cead5f69.mp4?t=1759491646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>email: <a href=\"mailto:deformeddreams@gmail.com\">deformeddreams@gmail.com</a></i></p>",
